msgid ""
"You can download the finished project for this part here: :download:"
"`Godot_FPS_Part_5.zip <files/Godot_FPS_Part_5.zip>`"
msgstr ""
"您可以在此处下载此部分的完成项目：:download:`Godot_FPS_Part_5.zip <files/"
"Godot_FPS_Part_5.zip>`"
